  <para>
    AKA Shaman, Witch doctor, Wiseman
  </para>
  <para>
    Table of Contents
  </para>
  <para>
    Description
  </para>
  <para>
    Becoming a Shaman
  </para>
  <para>
    Constraints
  </para>
  <para>
    Benefits
  </para>
  <para>
