  <para>
    Factors involved in the Application of the Energy Target type
    describes whether the energies affect a target, multiple targets, or
    no targets at all. A Target Type is what the spell is directed at. A
    spell with no Target Type is directed at the energy used in the
    spell. A ``Summon Fire'' spell has no target type. A ``Blast'Em''
    spell has a target type.
  </para>
  <para>
    No Target The spell is not intended to effect anything other than
    the base energy type used in the spell.
  </para>
  <para>
    Target,Self The spell is intended to effect the caster.
