  </para>
  <para>
    Multiple Targets The spell is intended to effect multiple targets.
    The assumption here is that the Quantitative Effect is {\bf split}
    between the multiple targets wheareas an Area of Effect spell has
    that Quantitative Effect apply equally among all of the targets.
  </para>
  <para>
    Area of Effect The spell is intended to effect everything in a given
    area.
